node.text:
FAITH 97m Feadship in #portofino🇮🇹 

Guests disembarking onto Wajer 55 chase boat (16m / 52ft with a top speed of 40knots). 

FAITH was delivered in 2017 and at 320ft she is the 5th largest Feadship on the water. 

Designed by RDW of London she is one of the sexiest yachts too. With her sleek curves and glass bottom swimming pool 👙which bathes light into her amazing beach club below which featured a full bar 🍹

Her foredeck features a helicopter 🚁 landing pad and a hangar to store it away. 

She is for charter at €1.5m per week & expenses

Like & Follow us @topyacht 

🗣 Is she your favourite Feadship?
